</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A <fr:em><fr:strong>precategory</fr:strong></fr:em> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> is specified by the following data:</fr:p><fr:ol><fr:li>a type <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[  \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex> of <fr:em>objects</fr:em>, written <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[c\in  C]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y\in  C]]></fr:tex> a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-001J.xml"
addr="erct-001J"
title="Sets">set</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[C  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y\right \rparen \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex> of <fr:em>arrows</fr:em>, written <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  C]]></fr:tex>, an <fr:em>identity arrow</fr:em> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[1_{x}\colon  x\to  x]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g\colon  y\to  z]]></fr:tex>, a <fr:em>composite arrow</fr:em> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[g\circ  f\colon  x \to  z]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>such that composition is associative and unital with respect to identity arrows:
    <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[       \boldsymbol {\lambda }_{f}\colon  1_{y}\circ  f = f\quad        \boldsymbol {\rho }_{f}\colon  f\circ  1_{x} = f \quad        \boldsymbol {\alpha }_{f,g,h}\colon    \mathopen {}\left \lparen h\circ  g\right \rparen \mathclose {} \circ  f = h\circ   \mathopen {}\left \lparen g\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}      ]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ol></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
