href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000I.agda">erct-000I.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A <fr:em><fr:strong>functor</fr:strong></fr:em> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F\colon  C\to  D]]></fr:tex> from a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-000B.xml"
addr="erct-000B"
title="Precategory">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[C]]></fr:tex> to a <fr:link
type="local"
href="erct-000B.xml"
addr="erct-000B"
title="Precategory">precategory</fr:link> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[D]]></fr:tex> is defined by the following data:</fr:p><fr:ol><fr:li>a function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[  \mathopen {}\left \lvert F\right \rvert \mathclose {} \colon    \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {} \to   \mathopen {}\left \lvert D\right \rvert \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex> giving the <fr:em>action of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> on objects</fr:em>, where we shall write <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Fx]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[  \mathopen {}\left \lvert F\right \rvert \mathclose {} x]]></fr:tex> given <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x\in  C]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for each <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[x,y\in  C]]></fr:tex> a function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F_{x,y} \colon  C  \mathopen {}\left \lparen x,y\right \rparen \mathclose {}  \to  D  \mathopen {}\left \lparen Fx,Fy\right \rparen \mathclose {} ]]></fr:tex> giving the <fr:em>action of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F]]></fr:tex> on arrows</fr:em>, where we shall write <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Ff\colon  Fx\to  Fy]]></fr:tex> for <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[F_{x,y}f]]></fr:tex> given <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  x\to  y]]></fr:tex>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>such that the action on morphisms commutes with identities and compositions:
    <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[       F^{1_{x}}\colon  F1_{x} = 1_{Fx}\quad        F^{g\circ  f}\colon  F  \mathopen {}\left \lparen g\circ  f\right \rparen \mathclose {}  = Fg\circ  Ff     ]]></fr:tex></fr:li></fr:ol></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
